aWA&d=URf6w8uoa5pE75%2FHQ8q7QXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=db6b6b29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8x3e2V6VaWA</a><br />\n<br />\n唔係Rap，但係掂嘅話，唔用autotune都係掂"},{"pid":"cc4dfef62d2baf199eee15bedef4932be308585c","tid":835571,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6b870ad4c69a10ac7dea7ae6946c93e1be34ce","tid":835571,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b99933436798534a50f4da8851978007784ff234","tid":835571,"uid":130950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T18:01:09.000Z","msg":"係exo個陣都自大開<br />\n唔係點會俾人恰到退隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"先澄清一樣嘢，前隊友無恰過佢，佢未走之前都受前隊友歡迎架。歌詞分配同隊形就無得好講係公司安排。<br />\n<br />\n佢嗰陣走係因為徐靜蕾想開戲畀佢，但拍嘅時間推正EXO第一次世巡，唔會有時間被佢拍戲，就幫佢推咗。徐靜蕾講明無佢套戲就唔開，又可以幫佢搭到路去支那，佢搵到靠山就同SM解約<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}